data.description: Welcome to your dream retreat at Windsor Green, where every day feels like a vacation! This stunning third-floor condo is turn key and fully furnished. Features include 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, and vaulted ceilings that make the living space feel open and airy. Perfect for Primary Residence, Vacation Getaway, or Investment. Picture yourself enjoying the view of the golf course from your private balcony after a busy day. Your new Myrtle Beach retreat is the perfect combination of lifestyle and location. Windsor Green is nestled in the heart of Carolina Forest, offering a prime location with easy access to schools, fantastic dining options, healthcare facilities, and more. Contact me today for a private tour!
